                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18121028-44-off247 t18121028-44-cd248"></join>, sixty-nine pounds weight of brass, value 3 l. and two pounds weight of lead, value 6 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18121028-44-victim600" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Lee
                  <interp inst="t18121028-44-victim600" type="surname" value="Lee"></interp>
